DESCRIPTION:Join us on the first Sunday of every month for SUNDAY SWING NIGHT at Hall of the Above \nWith music from swing band Death and Taxes (new in March) \nJasmine Worrell\, the Bay Area’s top swing dance instructor\, will offer a class from 4:15 – 5:00 \n👯 Followed by live music and an open dance floor until 7:00 PM \n🎟️ $25 for admission includes the class — tickets at the link below\, or cash at the door. (Eventbrite has a fee\, which you can avoid by paying at the door!) \n🕺🏾 See you on the dance floor!
