SUMMARY:Karaoke Sundays with Razor Entertainment - Hosted by AJ the KJ
DESCRIPTION:Weekly Sunday Karaoke at Barrel Proof Lounge! Hosted by AJ the KJ. Starts at 8PM — bring your voice & your friends!\nPresented by Razor Entertainment | Hosted by AJ the KJ\nYour new Sunday night ritual is here — Karaoke Night at Barrel Proof Lounge \, right in the heart of downtown Santa Rosa.\nHosted by the one and only AJ the KJ \, and powered by Razor Entertainment \, this weekly sing-along throwdown brings the perfect mix of talent\, fun\, and weekend wind-down vibes. Whether you’re a stage regular or a first-timer\, there’s a mic with your name on it.\n🎶 Massive karaoke catalog\n🎛️ Pro sound and smooth hosting 🍻 Beer\, 🍷 wine\, & refreshing Sabe cocktails 💃 Welcoming\, no-pressure atmosphere\n🗓️ Every Sunday\n🕖 8PM start\n📍 Barrel Proof Lounge — 501 Mendocino Ave\, Santa Rosa\n🔞 21+ only | 🎟️ No Cover\nBring your friends\, bring your voice\, and let’s make Sunday nights sing.\nCheck out www.BarrelProofLounge.com for all sorts of good times ahead!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/karaoke-sundays-with-razor-entertainment-hosted-by-aj-the-kj-16/
LOCATION:Barrel Proof Lounge\, 501 Mendocino Avenue\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.44260;-122.71573
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Barrel Proof Lounge 501 Mendocino Avenue Santa Rosa CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=501 Mendocino Avenue:geo:-122.71573,38.44260
END:VEVENT
