SUMMARY:Candlelight: The Best of Hans Zimmer
DESCRIPTION:Candlelight concerts bring the magic of a live\, multi-sensory musical experience to awe-inspiring locations like never seen before in Sonoma County. Get your tickets now to discover the music of 90s Unplugged at Sebastiani Theatre under the gentle glow of candlelight. \nGeneral Info\nVenue: Sebastiani Theatre\nDuration: 60 minutes. Doors open 45 minutes before the show. No entry once it starts.\nAge requirement: 8 years old or older. Anyone under the age of 16 must be accompanied by an adult\nAccessibility: this venue is ADA compliant\nSeating is assigned on a first come first served basis in each zone \nTentative Program\nTime from Inception\nThis Land from The Lion King\nZooster’s Breakout from Madagascar\nSupermarine from Dunkirk\nHonor from The Pacific\nA Dark Knight from The Dark Knight\nWonder Woman Suite\nGladiator Suite\nCornfield Chase from Interstellar\nDune Suite\nDiscombobulate from Sherlock Holmes\nPirates of the Caribbean Suite
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/candlelight-the-best-of-hans-zimmer/
LOCATION:Sebastiani Theatre\, 476 First Street East\, Sonoma\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Candlelihjy-listeso-string-quartet.jpg
GEO:38.2923;-122.456
