SUMMARY:Conversation with Dr. Caroline Collins at the Museum of Sonoma County
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a special evening at the Museum of Sonoma County with Dr. Caroline Collins\, curator of Take Me to the Water: Histories of the Black Pacific. Collins will be in conversation at the museum\, sharing insights into the exhibition’s themes\, curatorial process\, and the stories behind the work. \nConversation followed by audience Q&A.
