SUMMARY:Pasaflora\, Basilisk & Sloan Irving at HopMonk Sebastopol
DESCRIPTION:ABOUT: \nPASAFLORA (HEADLINER) \nPasaflora is a vibrant ensemble of college musicians who blend Soul\, R&B\, Blues\, and Jazz into their signature sound. The young group focuses on their electrifying live performances and longer jams. \nBASILISK (SUPPORT) \nBasilisk is a genre defying Sonoma County based quintet. They blur the lines between Jazz\, R&B\, Classical\, Hip-Hop\, and everything in between. They bring a little something for everyone and are bound to get the crowd moving. \nSLOAN IRVING (OPENER) \nSloan Irving is a singer songwriter from Petaluma. She pulls inspiration from many genres like Americana\, soul\, and indie rock while leaning heavily into her love of simple but haunting folk melodies and her desire to capture many sides of the human experience through her storytelling.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/pasaflora-basilisk-sloan-irving-at-hopmonk-sebastopol/
LOCATION:HopMonk Tavern – Sebastopol\, 230 Petaluma Ave\, Sebastopol\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
